0011EC  1               ; show_title_sprites — enable one sprite of each type at fixed
0011EC  1               ;   title-screen positions and print score labels beside them.
0011EC  1               ;
0011EC  1               ;   In VERA 640x480 space, 1 text row/col = 16 VERA pixels.
0011EC  1               ;   Sprites: X=96 (col 6), score labels at col 9.
0011EC  1               ;   Sprite 11 (Type C): Y=112 → text row 7,  "= 30 PTS"
0011EC  1               ;   Sprite 22 (Type B): Y=160 → text row 10, "= 20 PTS"
0011EC  1               ;   Sprite 44 (Type A): Y=208 → text row 13, "= 10 PTS"
