001A54  1               ; Explosion sprite pixel data — 16x16 4bpp, 128 bytes
001A54  1               ; Color 1 = white (bright core), Color 6 = yellow (burst), 0 = transparent
001A54  1               ; Starburst pattern, symmetric about centre.
